YOU KNOW EVERYTHING

487
00:28:54,640 --> 00:28:57,000
ABOUT BRUISES, SPRAINS,
AND CHARLEY HORSES.

488
00:28:57,040 --> 00:28:58,440
JUST GET
YOUR VON STEINER

489
00:28:58,480 --> 00:28:59,880
TO GET ME
SOME BANDAGES,

490
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:01,280
SOME LINIMENT,
OIL, TAPES,

491
00:29:01,320 --> 00:29:03,000
WE'RE IN BUSINESS.

492
00:29:06,280 --> 00:29:08,320
I DON'T WANT
A TRAINER.

493
00:29:09,320 --> 00:29:10,720
COLBY,
