526
00:31:09,440 --> 00:31:10,800
COLBY.

527
00:31:10,880 --> 00:31:12,240
HATCH, THE TRAINER.

528
00:31:12,320 --> 00:31:14,320
HELLO. HOW ARE YOU?

529
00:31:15,200 --> 00:31:16,080
