866
00:58:12,040 --> 00:58:13,760
GOOD-BYE.

867
00:58:13,800 --> 00:58:14,880
<i>SALUT.</i>

868
00:58:18,320 --> 00:58:19,360
<i>AU REVOIR, RENEE.</i>

869
00:58:19,440 --> 00:58:20,480
