TO BE MY FRIEND?

885
00:59:05,520 --> 00:59:07,200
I DIDN'T WANT
TO HEAR YOUR NAME.

886
00:59:07,240 --> 00:59:09,040
AND NOW THAT I DO,
I DON'T WANT TO HEAR

887
00:59:09,120 --> 00:59:10,960
ANYTHING ELSE ABOUT YOU.

888
00:59:11,040 --> 00:59:12,640
THE LESS I KNOW,
THE BETTER IT IS FOR YOU.

889
00:59:12,720 --> 00:59:13,680
AND FOR YOU?

890
00:59:13,760 --> 00:59:15,200
AND FOR ME, TOO.

891
00:59:15,280 --> 00:59:17,600
