YOUR FRIENDS IN A TOUGH SPOT.

892
00:59:17,640 --> 00:59:19,360
IS THAT WHY YOU'RE MAD?

893
00:59:19,400 --> 00:59:20,640
I'M NOT MAD.

894
00:59:20,680 --> 00:59:23,040
BUT BEING IN A TOUGH
SPOT, AS YOU CALL IT,

895
00:59:23,080 --> 00:59:24,960
