HOW DO I FEEL?

898
00:59:29,400 --> 00:59:32,280
I FEEL RESPONSIBLE,
HOPEFUL.

899
00:59:32,320 --> 00:59:33,520
WHEN I GET WORD

900
00:59:33,600 --> 00:59:36,000
THAT SOMEONE I SHELTERED
IS SAFE, THEN I'M HAPPY.

901
00:59:36,040 --> 00:59:37,480
I CAN FORGET THEM.

902
00:59:37,560 --> 00:59:38,920
BUT WHEN I HEAR

903
00:59:39,000 --> 00:59:41,320
THAT THEY'VE
BEEN CAUGHT OR KILLED,

904
00:59:41,400 --> 00:59:43,000
THEN I
REMEMBER EVERYTHING.

905
00:59:43,040 --> 00:59:45,400
I REMEMBER THEIR FACE,
THEIR VOICES,

906
00:59:45,440 --> 00:59:49,000
WHAT THEY SAID
ABOUT THEIR PARENTS,

907
00:59:49,080 --> 00:59:52,360
THEIR CHILD, THEIR PETS,
AND I MOURN FOR THEM.

908
00:59:52,440 --> 00:59:55,320
I DON'T WANT
TO MOURN FOR YOU.

909
00:59:55,360 --> 00:59:57,760
WELL, YOU'RE SAFE
WITH ME, RENEE.

910
00:59:57,840 --> 00:59:59,400
HOW?

911
00:59:59,480 --> 01:00:04,200
WELL, I'M, UH...
AN ORPHAN, A BASTARD.

912
01:00:04,280 --> 01:00:06,280
